# Filter Fun 

A simple image filter web app.

## What it does
- Upload an image
- Apply filters like grayscale, blur, sepia
- Preview changes instantly

## Tech
- TypeScript / JavaScript
- HTML + CSS
- Express backend (optional version)

## Purpose
Built for learning full-stack development and UI design.



<details>
  <summary>Click to see project details</summary>

### About this project
This is a full-stack image filter app where users can upload images and apply filters like grayscale, blur, and sepia.

### Features
- Upload images
- Apply filters in real time
- Save images to gallery
- Download images

### Tech used
- React / TypeScript
- Node.js + Express
- PostgreSQL (Drizzle ORM)

